  "title": "Automatically generate the widget usages",
  "body": "I think we could make our JSDoc parser generate the `usage` as well to ensure we keep them always synchronized and DRY.\n\n``` js\nconst usage = require('./usage');\n```\n\n``` js\nmodule.exports = `Usage:\n@function({\n  @mandatoryArg,\n  [...]\n  [ @optionalArg=@defaultValue ],\n  [ [...] ]\n})`;\n```\n",
